📦 E-Commerce Database System
________________________________________
🚀 Project Overview
  
This project is a fully designed and normalized E-Commerce Database System built using Microsoft SQL Server (SSMS).
It simulates a real-world online retail platform and supports:
•	Customer management 
•	Product catalog 
•	Order processing 
•	Payment handling 
•	Shipping & logistics 
•	Inventory tracking 
•	Reviews & ratings 
•	Coupons & discounts 
•	Audit logging 
In addition to database design and analytics, the project is extended with Python-based Data Analysis (EDA) and Machine Learning models using Neural Networks.
The system is also Power BI ready for interactive dashboards and business intelligence reporting.
________________________________________
🎯 Key Features
  
✔ Fully normalized relational database (3NF)
✔ Scalable schema design using multiple schemas
✔ Strong foreign key relationships for data integrity
✔ Advanced indexing for performance optimization
✔ Audit logging for security and tracking
✔ Business intelligence ready (Power BI + EDA)
✔ AI-powered analytics extension using Neural Networks
✔ Real-world e-commerce simulation
________________________________________
🏗️ Database Architecture
  
The database is structured into the following schemas:
Schema	Description
People	Users, authentication, roles
Products	Product catalog, categories, reviews
Sales	Orders, order items, shopping cart, coupons
Finance	Payments and transactions
Logistics	Shipping and delivery tracking
System	Audit logs and system monitoring
